fields.Description: Affects physical damage dealt by gladiator's arms, marauder's arms, dark knight's arms, gunbreaker's arms, pugilist's arms, lancer's arms, samurai's arms, reaper's arms, thaumaturge's arms, arcanist's arms, red mage's arms, pictomancer's arms, conjurer's arms, astrologian's arms, sage's arms, and blue mage's arms.
fields.Name: Strength

fields.Description: Affects the rate at which your physical and magic attacks land direct hits, dealing slightly more damage than normal hits. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be direct. Higher values will also result in greater damage for actions which guarantee direct hits.
fields.Name: Direct Hit Rate

fields.Description: Affects the amount of physical and magic damage dealt, as well as HP restored. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be critical/higher the potency of critical hits.
fields.Name: Critical Hit

fields.Description: Upon the back of this crystal plaque are engraved the myriad creations of blacksmiths from eras past.
fields.Name: Soul of the Blacksmith

fields.Description:
This crystalline prism captures the likeness of a piece of equipment and projects it onto another object of comparable form and function.

[Necessary to project glamours.]
fields.Name: Glamour Prism

fields.Description:
It has recently been discovered that this substance of unknown origin has the faculty to assimilate with other forms of matter, effectively restoring them to their original condition. This specific grade of dark matter has been shown to bond best with precisely crafted items made from high-quality materials.

[Used to repair equipment for levels 1-100.]
fields.Name: Grade 8 Dark Matter
